text: Hagen Reinhold (born 23 March 1978) is a German politician. He was born in Wismar. He is a member of the Free Democratic Party (FDP). Reinhold has served as a member of the Bundestag from the state of Mecklenburg-Vorpommern from 2017 to 2023.
